\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cactus_Flower\" title=\"Cactus Flower\"><img alt=\"Cactus Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cactus_Flower.png?61617a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Floral_Shirt\" title=\"Floral Shirt\"><img alt=\"Floral Shirt.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Floral_Shirt.png?a921bc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/64px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\"><img alt=\"Papyrus.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Papyrus.png?5e1602\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Silk\" title=\"Silk\"><img alt=\"Silk.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Silk.png?22ef7f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Petals\" title=\"Petals\"><img alt=\"Petals.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Petals.png?d5ab74\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Floral_Shirt\" title=\"Floral Shirt\"><img alt=\"Floral Shirt.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Floral_Shirt.png?a921bc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\"><img alt=\"Papyrus.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Papyrus.png?5e1602\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Worker\" title=\"Pig Worker\"><img alt=\"Pig Worker.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pig_Worker.png/42px-Pig_Worker.png?f06d7c\" width=\"42\" height=\"62\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oinc\" title=\"Oinc\"><img alt=\"Oinc.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Oinc.png?bf1bac\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In the old research system, the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Research_points_list\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Research points list\">research cost</a> of Papyrus was 30.</li>\n<li>Despite being made out of four <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Reeds\" title=\"Cut Reeds\">Cut Reeds</a>, Papyrus has the same burn time as one.</li>\n<li>Papyrus is a thin paper-like material made from the pith of Cyperus Papyrus, a species of reed native to Africa, also called the paper reed.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_papyrus.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_papyrus.png/120px-CD_papyrus.png?84a258\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DST-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#DST-0\">DST</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DS-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#DS-0\">DS</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"RoG-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#RoG-0\">RoG</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"SW-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#SW-0\">SW</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Ham-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus#Ham-0\">Ham</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n <p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
