  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Papyrus.png\n|image = Papyrus Dropped.png\n|tier = 1\n|canBeBurned=1\n|tab = Refine\n|ingredient1 = Cut Reeds\n|multiplier1 = 4|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 15 sec.\n|stack = 40\n|description = For writing things\n|droppedBy ={{Pic24|Shipwrecked icon}}: {{Pic32|X Marks The Spot}}\n|soldBy ={{Pic|24|Hamlet icon}}: {{Pic32|The Tinkerer's Tower}} ({{Pic|24|Oinc}} &times;1)\n|spawnCode = \"papyrus\"\n|perk = Used to make [[Books]] among other things}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Some sheets of paper.\n|willow = I bet it'd burn!\n|wolfgang = Is like paper.\n|wendy = For documenting my pain.\n|wx78 = I PREFER DOT MATRIX PAPER\n|wickerbottom = Thin sheets of cellulose and lignin.\n|woodie = I'd rather chop than write.\n|maxwell = A blank canvas.\n|wagstaff = This paper has interesting clothlike properties.\n|wigfrid = This will carry förth the recörd öf my saga.\n|webber = We could do our homework.\n|walani = Bet this burns good.\n|warly = I could write down my recipes on this.\n|woodlegs = Aye! A fresh map!\n|wilba = WILBA CAN'ST BE POET NOW\n|wormwood = Flat friends\n|wheeler = Dear Diary, today I made paper.\n|winona = I don't have much use for that, personally.\n|wortox = An ancient scroll in the making.\n|wurt = Make more stories, Wicker-lady!\n|walter = Just some paper with nothing on it.\n|wanda = I should really write things down before I forget them...\n|choose = wilson}}\n'''Papyrus''', also known as '''Paper''', is a [[Refined]] [[Item]] crafted with 4 [[Cut Reeds]]. A [[Science Machine]] is required to unlock the recipe. Papyrus can be used to make [[Honey Poultice]] for healing as well as a [[Birdcage]], [[Night Armor]], and [[Compass]]. [[Wickerbottom]] can use it to craft [[Books]] and starts out with two Papyrus. Papyrus can be used to fuel [[Campfire]]s, though it has a low burn time.\n\n== {{Pic32|Gift Icon}} Downloadable Content ==\nIn the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' and ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLCs, Papyrus is one of the ingredients to craft a [[Floral Shirt]]. [[Webber]] can use Papyrus to craft [[Spider Eggs]].\n\n== {{Pic32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|item2 = Gold Nugget\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Compass}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|item2 = Honey\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Honey Poultice}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|item2 = Beeswax\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Wax Paper}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Egg\n|count2 = 2\n|result = Birds of the World\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Seeds\n|item3 = Manure\n|result = Applied Horticulture\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Sleepytime Stories\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Tentacle Spots\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = On Tentacles\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Red Gem\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = The End is Nigh\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Obsidian\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Joy of Volcanology\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 5\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = Night Armour}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Gold Nugget\n|count2 = 6\n|item3 = Seeds\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Birdcage}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 6\n|item2 = Spider Gland\n|count2 = 6\n|item3 = Silk\n|count3 = 12\n|result = Spider Eggs\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n|character = Webber}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Silk\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Cactus Flower\n|count3 = 5\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Floral Shirt\n|dlc = Reign of Giants}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Silk\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Petals\n|count3 = 5\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Floral Shirt\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Papyrus\n|tool = Pig Worker\n|result = Oinc\n|resultcount = 2\n|dlc = Hamlet}}\n\n== {{Pic32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* In the old research system, the [[Research points list|research cost]] of Papyrus was 30.\n* Despite being made out of four [[Cut Reeds]], Papyrus has the same burn time as one.\n* Papyrus is a thin paper-like material made from the pith of Cyperus Papyrus, a species of reed native to Africa, also called the paper reed.\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nCD papyrus.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\n</gallery>\n<tabber>\nResources=\n{{Resources}}\n|-|\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items}}\n</tabber>\n[[Category:Science]]\n[[Category:Refine Tab]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]"
